00:20:26.200 --> 00:20:27.233
My girlfriend, you know,
my girlfriend, Hope,

378
00:20:27.266 --> 00:20:28.802
she's into that kind of stuff.

379
00:20:29.970 --> 00:20:31.705
And you believe
in all that stuff?

380
