00:23:53.173 --> 00:23:55.842
I found these in my
husband's nightstand.

436
00:23:55.876 --> 00:23:57.443
I thought maybe Carla done them,

437
00:23:57.476 --> 00:23:59.947
but I knew deep down he hadn't.

