00:31:49.048 --> 00:31:50.818
Yeah, I'm fine, you scared me.

521
00:31:51.719 --> 00:31:52.520
Okay, hun.

522
00:31:52.553 --> 00:31:53.953
You coming upstairs?

523
00:31:55.623 --> 00:31:57.924
Yeah, I'm just gonna get
